These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, chess, drawing, reading
4 different pets are kept: snake, bird, chinchilla, pony
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the bird##2
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
3. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##8
4. the owner of the bird is not the person who's hobby is drawing##6
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | reading  | camping | drawing | chess  |
| Pet   | snake | chinchilla   | pony  | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, tomato, watermelon, zucchini
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, blue, emerald, grey
1. the person who likes grey is not to the left of the person who likes grey##8
2. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the right of the person eating zucchini##5
3. the person eating grapes is the person who likes blue##1
4. the person eating zucchini is between the person eating grapes and the person eating tomato##2
5. the person eating tomato is somewhere between the person eating watermelon and the person who likes chestnut##7
6. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5
7. the person who likes chestnut is not to the left of the person who likes chestnut##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | watermelon | tomato          | zucchini | grapes     |
| Color    | emerald      | grey | chestnut | blue |

