.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, disco, metal, rock
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, hiking, puzzles, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is not to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the fan of disco##1
4. the fan of rock is not to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8
5. the fan of blues is the person who's hobby is chess##1
6. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
7. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | disco         | rock   | blues    |
| Hobby         | hiking | card-games | puzzles | chess |

