.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, february, november, december
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, indie, pop
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
5. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
6. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
7. the person who's birthday is in december is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Birthday          | december | march | february  | november |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | pop         | indie | ambient |

