2. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
3. the fan of trance is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the fan of trance##7
5. the fan of disco is not to the right of the fan of electronic##8
6. the fan of electronic is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the fan of disco##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Music-Genre     | trance | disco | electronic | gospel     |
| Sport   | baseball   | rugby        | tennis          | ice-hockey |

