.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, bird, pony, chinchilla
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, bus, taxi, trike
1. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person driving the boat##2
2. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
4. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
5. the person driving the bus is the person driving the bus##1
6. the owner of the pony is not the person driving the taxi##6
7. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
8. the person driving the boat is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Pet   | chinchilla   | mouse | pony | bird |
| Transport     | trike | bus       | boat  | taxi    |

