2. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the right of the person eating lime##8
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person eating pineapple##5
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating onion is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's sport is baseball##2
6. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
7. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | lime        | pineapple | onion      | corn    |
| Sport   | soccer | baseball   | biathlon | cricket |

