.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, juice, soy-milk
House: townhouse, cottage, gothic-revival, art-deco
1. the art-deco house is not to the right of the townhouse house##8
2. the art-deco house is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8
3. the cottage house is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
6. the townhouse house is somewhere between the gothic-revival house and the person drinking fanta##7
7. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | fanta         | juice    | cola       |
| House      | cottage | art-deco | townhouse | gothic-revival |

