3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the person who growssunflower##5
4. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who growssunflower and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
5. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
