.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, papaya, watermelon, zucchini
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, white, black, blood-red
 1. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the left of the person who likes black##5
 2. the person eating zucchini is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
 3. the person eating grapefruit is the person who likes black##1
 4. the person who likes black is not to the right of the person who likes white##8
 5. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 6. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 7. the person who likes white is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the person who likes black##8
 9. the person who likes white is not to the left of the person eating grapefruit##8
10. the person eating papaya is not to the left of the person who likes lilac##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | papaya    | watermelon | grapefruit | zucchini |
| Color   | lilac | blood-red  | black     | white    |

