.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
House: gothic-revival, townhouse, palace, tower
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, subway, van
1. the person driving the jet-ski is not the gothic-revival house##6
2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the tower house is not to the left of the person driving the van##8
4. the palace house is the person driving the car##1
5. the tower house is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the car##7
6. the tower house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
7. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the van and the palace house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| House         | townhouse    | tower | gothic-revival | palace |
| Transport   | jet-ski | van      | subway     | car     |

 